'''Trans-Zone Development and Exploitation Consortium''' was a [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] owned company that carried out its operations in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] to evade scrutiny. This was because the company was in actuality a front for a Huttese [[Gambling/Legends|gambling]] syndicate. The company tried to show an air of legitimacy while running its operation in a behind the scenes fashion.

